# agent Directory Guide

The [agent/](mdc:agent) directory contains logic for agent-based reasoning and orchestration, including:

- [canvas.py](mdc:agent/canvas.py): Main agent canvas and workflow logic.
- [settings.py](mdc:agent/settings.py): Agent configuration settings.
- [component/](mdc:agent/component): Individual agent components (retrieval, search, translation, etc.).
- [templates/](mdc:agent/templates): Agent templates.
- [test/](mdc:agent/test): Agent-related tests.
- [README.md](mdc:agent/README.md): Agent module documentation.

See each referenced file or subdirectory for more details on agent logic and components.
